      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it's honestly such a gem. It\u2019s been super well-loved and is running beautifully\u2014perfect for someone looking for a reliable car that still looks and feels great on the road. I've kept up with all the maintenance, so it's totally ready for your next big adventure. I'd love for it to go to a good home, so come by and take it for a test drive!",
