    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sorted E46 M3, featuring the high-strung S54 inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including a complete VANOS system overhaul and documented rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity under high lateral G-loads. The Getrag six-speed manual transmission shifts precisely, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. While the exterior reflects its life as a celebrated driver's car, the suspension geometry remains true with refreshed bushings and dampers, offering the tactile feedback and balanced weight distribution this chassis is renowned for.",
      "price": 34500.0,
