    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained 2015 Porsche Cayman in classic Agate Grey Metallic. This vehicle strikes the perfect balance for a driver who wants peak performance without the 'garage queen' anxiety. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though a few minor stone chips on the front fascia tell the story of spirited weekend drives. Inside, the black leather interior remains smoke-free and firm, with only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Mechanically, she is sound; the 2.7L flat-six pulls smoothly through every gear, and the service records are comprehensive, including a recent brake fluid flush and oil change. All electronics, from the responsive infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control, function exactly as they should. It is a turn-key enthusiast car, offering a tight, rattle-free ride and the unmistakable exhaust note of a well-cared-for mid-engine masterpiece.",
      "price": 34500.0,
